<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en-US">
<head>
  <title>Brave UX - Work - Livesafe</title>
  <%- include ../partials/_head %>
</head>
<body>
  <main class="wrapper case-study livesafe">
    <header class="case-header">
      <div class="case-header-content container">
        <h5 class="case-header-client-name">Livesafe</h5>
        <h1 class="case-header-tagline">&lsquo;Safety First&rsquo; in&nbsp;<br />the digital age</h1>
        <h6 class="case-header-type">User-Centric Safety Mobile App</h6>
      </div>
    </header>

    <section class="case-exec-summary padded light-blue">
      <div class="container">
        <p class="case-exec-summary-text">We designed a testable prototype to promote LiveSafe&rsquo;s long-term business goals and create a better in-app experience for users.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="case-breakdown padded blue">
      <div class="container row">
        <div class="case-breakdown-box column gutter">
          <p class="case-breakdown-heading">Challenge</p>
          <h3 class="case-breakdown-summary">
            Distinguishing LiveSafe from a user&rsquo;s organization
          </h3>
          <p class="case-breakdown-detail">
            Who is LiveSafe? Users are confused by who owns each feature in the app and LiveSafe gets lost in the mix.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="case-breakdown-box column gutter">
          <p class="case-breakdown-heading">Solution</p>
          <h3 class="case-breakdown-summary">
            Clarifying who&rsquo;s the boss
          </h3>
          <p class="case-breakdown-detail">
            The new prototype clearly differentiates LiveSafe from the organizations using the app.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="case-breakdown-box column gutter">
          <p class="case-breakdown-heading">Scope</p>
          <ul class="case-breakdown-list">
            <li class="case-breakdown-list-item">Information Architecture</li>
            <li class="case-breakdown-list-item">Mobile App Design</li>
            <li class="case-breakdown-list-item">Prototype Testing</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="block padded-top gray overflow">
      <div class="row container">
        <div class="inner-block column column-block half-md one-third-lg livesafe-homepage">
          <img data-normal="./images/work/livesafe/mobile-homepage-bg.svg" alt="" class="inner-block-image contain">
          <div class="frame frame-mobile darker shadow absolute sr-left">
            <div class="frame-container">
                <img data-normal="./images/work/livesafe/mobile-homepage.jpg" alt="" class="inner-block-image">
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="inner-block absolute-center-md order-top-xs column half-md two-third-lg">
          <div class="inner-block-content gutter-left padded-bottom">
            <h2 class="case-block-heading">A proper&nbsp;<br />starting point</h2>
            <p class="case-block-text">
              The new homepage and bottom navigation provide the user with everything they need in one, easy to find place. The newsfeed shows recent updates while the map orients the user, providing a natural entry point into SafeWalk.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="block">
      <img data-normal="./images/work/livesafe/pedestrians.jpg" alt="" class="block-image">
    </section>

    <section class="block row">
      <div class="inner-block absolute-center-md padded column half-md blue">
        <div class="inner-block-content container">
          <h2 class="case-block-heading">Don&rsquo;t be a bystander</h2>
          <p class="case-block-text">
            LiveSafe&rsquo;s app empowers users to anonymously or publicly report tips to their organization&rsquo;s security team. Users&rsquo; can attach photos or videos, then message security with more details to do their part in keeping themselves and others safe.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="inner-block column column-block align-self-center half-md gray hide-overflow livesafe-security">
        <div class="lazy-ratio" data-width="136" data-height="150">
          <img data-normal="./images/work/livesafe/mobile-security-bg.svg" alt="" class="inner-block-image">
        </div>
        <div class="frame frame-mobile darker shadow absolute sr-left">
          <div class="frame-container">
            <img data-normal="./images/work/livesafe/mobile-security1.jpg" alt="" class="inner-block-image">
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="frame frame-mobile darker shadow absolute sr-left sr-delay">
          <div class="frame-container">
            <img data-normal="./images/work/livesafe/mobile-security2.jpg" alt="" class="inner-block-image">
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="block padded">
      <div class="inner-block padded-bottom row absolute-center-md">
        <div class="inner-block-content content-centered container">
          <h2 class="case-block-heading">Know where you are</h2>
          <p class="case-block-text">
            We took a complicated map and simplified it, providing the user with additional information and better safety features. Campus buildings now have a context panel that links to related resources and users&rsquo; have an additional entry point into SafeWalk.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="inner-block row livesafe-nav">
        <div class="container-narrow">
          <div class="lazy-ratio" data-width="205" data-height="150">
            <img data-normal="./images/work/livesafe/mobile-nav-bg.svg" alt="" class="inner-block-image">
          </div>
          <div class="frame frame-mobile darker shadow absolute sr-right sr-delay">
            <div class="frame-container">
              <img data-normal="./images/work/livesafe/mobile-nav1.jpg" alt="" class="inner-block-image">
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="frame frame-mobile darker shadow absolute sr-bottom">
            <div class="frame-container">
              <img data-normal="./images/work/livesafe/mobile-nav2.jpg" alt="" class="inner-block-image">
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="frame frame-mobile darker shadow absolute sr-left sr-delay">
            <div class="frame-container">
              <img data-normal="./images/work/livesafe/mobile-nav3.jpg" alt="" class="inner-block-image">
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="block row dark-blue">
      <div class="inner-block column column-block align-self-center">
        <div class="lazy-ratio" data-width="1545" data-height="1557">
          <img data-normal="./images/work/livesafe/table-devices.jpg" alt="" class="inner-block-image">
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="inner-block absolute-center-md padded column half">
        <div class="inner-block-content container">
          <h2 class="case-block-heading">Proven by research</h2>
          <p class="case-block-text">
            We created an interactive mobile prototype and sat down with actual users, to explore their safety concerns, habits, and mental models. This data validated our approach, and identified refinements that we integrated into LiveSafe&rsquo;s product launch.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="block padded">
      <div class="row container">
        <div class="inner-block absolute-center-md gutter-bottom-mobile column half-md">
          <div class="inner-block-content gutter-right">
            <h2 class="case-block-heading">Resources when and where you need them</h2>
            <p class="case-block-text">
              Resources are great to have, but only if the user can find them. We gave a resources tab to keep them all organized and accessible.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="inner-block column column-block align-self-center half-md livesafe-resources">
          <div class="lazy-ratio" data-width="718" data-height="521">
            <img data-normal="./images/work/livesafe/mobile-resources-bg.svg" alt="" class="inner-block-image contain">
          </div>
          <div class="frame frame-mobile darker shadow absolute sr-stagger-left">
            <div class="frame-container">
              <img data-normal="./images/work/livesafe/mobile-resources1.jpg" alt="" class="inner-block-image">
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="frame frame-mobile darker shadow absolute sr-stagger-left">
            <div class="frame-container">
              <img data-normal="./images/work/livesafe/mobile-resources2.jpg" alt="" class="inner-block-image">
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="frame frame-mobile darker shadow absolute sr-stagger-left">
            <div class="frame-container">
              <img data-normal="./images/work/livesafe/mobile-resources3.jpg" alt="" class="inner-block-image">
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="block">
      <img data-normal="./images/work/livesafe/crosswalk.jpg" alt="" class="block-image">
    </section>
    
    <%- include ../partials/_footer-scripts %>
  </main>

</body>
</html>
